<figureCitation box="[1162,1243,439,464]" captionStart="FIGURE 20" captionStartId="36.[151,250,1360,1383]" captionTargetBox="[156,1430,451,1339]" captionTargetId="figure-430@36.[156,1431,451,1339]" captionTargetPageId="36" captionText="FIGURE 20. Distribution of Belomitra species. For Belomitra nesiotica and B. bouteti distribution areas and types localities are figured, not the individual collection sites. Type localities of B. brachymitra and B. hypsomitra off Fiji are marked with an arrow." pageId="50" pageNumber="51">
